	dprr:hasNoteText "Proposed a bill to confiscate the property of Servilius Ahala, accusing Minucius of false accusation, and Servilius of caedes civis indemnati (Liv. 4.21.3-4; cf. Cic. Dom. 86; Rep. 1.6; Val. Max. 5.3.2g; Rotondi 210f.). See 439, on Servilius and Minucius." .
